<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
      i18n:domain="launchpad">

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div class="portlet">
    <div class="portletBody portletContent">

      <img src="/++resource++info_icon.gif" />

      This page documents the HCT (Hypothetical Changeset Tool) status
      of the <span tal:replace="context/displayname">hoary
      foobar</span> package.  Use the links and information below to
      ensure that HCT correctly understands how this source package is
      connected to upstream.

    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="portlet">
    <div class="portletBody portletContent">

      <img src="/++resource++info_icon.gif" />
      In order for HCT to function effectively, we need to have the
      upstream branch published in the <a
      href="http://bazaar.canonical.com/">Bazaar revision control system</a>
      format.
    </div>
  </div>

</metal:leftportlets>

<metal:rightportlets fill-slot="portlets_two">
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-actions" />
  <div tal:replace="structure context/@@+portlet-hctstatus" />
</metal:rightportlets>


<div metal:fill-slot="main">

  <h2>Packaging data for <span tal:replace="context/displayname">foobar in
  hoary</span></h2>

  <p>HCT uses "packaging" information to link a source package in a
  distribution to upstream product series.</p>

  <p class="portalMessage" tal:condition="not: context/productseries">
    Unable to determine the upstream productseries for this package. Please
    add packaging information for this package!
  </p>

  <table class="listing"
         tal:condition="context/sourcepackagename/packagings">
    <caption>Packaging data for all source packages called
      "<span tal:replace="context/sourcepackagename/name">apache</span>"
    </caption>

    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Distribution</th>
        <th>Release</th>
        <th>Upstream Product Series</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>

    <tbody>
      <tr class="highlight" tal:condition="context/packaging">
        <td tal:content="context/packaging/distrorelease/distribution/displayname">
          ubuntu
        </td>
        <td tal:content="context/packaging/distrorelease/displayname">
          hoary
        </td>
        <td tal:content="context/packaging/productseries/title">
          evolution main
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tal:block repeat="packaging context/sourcepackagename/packagings">
          <tr tal:condition="python: packaging != context.packaging">
            <td tal:content="packaging/distrorelease/distribution/displayname">
              ubuntu
            </td>
            <td tal:content="packaging/distrorelease/displayname">
              hoary
            </td>
            <td tal:content="packaging/productseries/title">
              evolution main
            </td>
          </tr>
      </tal:block>
    </tbody>

  </table>

  <tal:block condition="context/productseries"
             define="ps context/productseries">

    <h2>Upstream Bazaar Status</h2>

    <div tal:replace="structure ps/@@+hctstatus-core" />

  </tal:block>

</div>
</body>
</html>
